        Parameters:
        modulePosition - The module's offset from the center of the robot's center of rotation
        angleOffset - An angle in radians that is used to offset the angle encoder
        angleMotor - The motor that controls the module's angle
        driveMotor - The motor that drives the module's wheel
        angleEncoder - The analog input for the angle encoder
